Genitalia. Surstyli symmetric, slightly curved at tip; ST8 with m.a. visible (
Fig. 8H
). Borders of SES uncertain, with numerous hairs at base of SS; gonopods small, symmetric; hypandrium narrow, elongated; phallic guide pointed and with lobes in ventral view (
Fig. 8L
) (curved towards SS in lateral view, 
Fig. 8G
); phallus trifid, tubes very thin; ejaculatory apodeme elongated funnel shaped; sperm pump vase shaped (
Fig. 8K
).
